data.eml:eml: A new species of Physalaemus (Anura, Leptodactylidae) from the Atlantic Forest of Misiones, northeastern Argentina

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cardozo, Dario E., Pereyra, Martin O. (2018): A new species of Physalaemus (Anura, Leptodactylidae) from the Atlantic Forest of Misiones, northeastern Argentina. Zootaxa 4387 (3): 580-590, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4387.3.10
